headline: NFP Acquires Hamilton Insurance Agency, Expanding Its Risk Management and Integrated Benefits Administration Capabilities
summary: NFP, an Aon company and leading property and casualty insurance broker (P&C) and benefits consultant, today announced the acquisition of Alan J. Zuccari, Inc. dba Hamilton Insurance Agency (Hamilton), a P&C broker and benefits administration provider located in Fairfax, Virginia.
